    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Bottles used for sprinkling scented water, spice, or pounce; often provided with devices which enable them to be suspended from chains.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
